  "texts": [
    "In this flow model, the Blockchain stores the data in a block so that the data are not being altered.",
    "The smart contract performs the task of analysis that is important to identify or control the management system.",
    "There are several risks related to Blockchain technology in the proposed Model.",
    "These include:",
    "Loss of Private Keys: In case of key loss the user of the system can not retrieve the password as there is no option for key recovery."
  ]
}